        <Parent_String>Felis catus (species) [300265960], Felis (genus) [300265717], Felidae (family) [300265716], Carnivora (order) [300310328], Mammalia (class) [300265707], Vertebrata (subphylum) [300265720], Chordata (phylum) [300266513], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
