    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Breed of domestic cat that originated in Thailand. It is characterized by a long body and tail, wedge-shaped head and slightly slanted blue eyes. Siamese are typically white or buff colored on the body with darker "points" on the tail, head, and feet, which may be dark brown (seal point), blue gray (blue point), milk-chocolate brown (chocolate point), pinkish gray (lilac point), or reddish orange (red point). The color and coat pattern are genetically recessive characteristics.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>源於泰國的家貓品種，其特徵為長的身體與尾巴、楔形頭部與稍微偏藍色的眼睛。暹羅貓通常為白色或暗黃色，而尾部、頭部、足部之「重點色」較深，可能是深棕色（海豹重點色）、藍灰色（藍色重點色）、牛奶巧克力色（巧克力重點色）、粉紅灰色（淡紫重點色）或紅橙色（紅色重點色），顏色與皮毛花紋在基因上是隱性特徵。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ras van huiskat afkomstig uit Thailand. De kat wordt gekenmerkt door een lang lichaam en staart, wigvormige kop en blauwe ogen. Siamese katten hebben typisch een witte vacht met donkerdere "points" op de staart, de kop en de poten, die donkerbruin (seal point), blauw (blue point), chocoladebruin (chocolate point), lila (lilac point), of rood (red point) kunnen zijn. De kleur en het vachtpatroon zijn genetisch recessieve kenmerken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
